Skills.Name: Leave It to Heaven
Skills.Description: Raises Hidden Technique DMG Inflicted for all allies within 150 cm of ally with highest ATK by {0}% for 15s. Raises DEF of all allies by <color=red>{1}%</color> for 15s.
Skills.ShortDescription: Raises Hidden Technique DMG Inflicted for all allies within range. Raises DEF of all allies

Skills.Name: Unrefined Person
Skills.Description: Inflicts 3-hit DMG ({0}% + {1}% + {2}%) on all enemies. Further lowers ATK by <color=red>{3}%</color> for 10s and cancels Buff effect if Yellow Elemental.
Skills.ShortDescription: Inflicts 3-hit DMG on all enemies, lowers ATK and cancels Buff effect(s) if Yellow Elemental

Skills.Name: Dazzling Royal Flush
Skills.Description: Recovers HP of all allies by {0}% of ATK. Also <code=200,param=115><color=#3398f1>shields</color> DMG (<color=red>{1}%</color> of skill user's ATK) for 30s. Further raises ATK by {3}% multiplied by number of Therianthropes in party for 15s.
Skills.ShortDescription: Recovers HP and shields DMG of all allies, raises ATK based on number of Therianthropes in party

Skills.Name: Strike Combo
Skills.Description: Reduces DMG Received for all allies by <color=red>5.00%-40.00%</color> for 5s according to Combo Bonus. Inflicts 100.00% DMG.
Skills.ShortDescription: Reduces DMG Received for all allies. Inflicts DMG on single enemy

Skills.Name: Dazzling Fox Girl
Skills.Description: At start of Wave, raises own DEF by <color=red>{1}%</color> multiplied by number of Therianthropes in party for 60s. Recovers SP of all allies by {4} if partied with 5 Green Elemental Therianthrope allies.
Skills.ShortDescription: At start of Wave, raises own DEF based on number of Therianthropes in party. Recovers SP of all allies if partied with 5 Green Elemental Therianthrope allies
